'''全球富豪榜'''（{{lang-en|The World's Billionaires}}）是[[美國|美國]]商業雜誌《[[富比士|富比士]]》自1987年3月起，在每年3月發布的全球[[亿万富翁|最富有人物]]的年度排行榜。<ref name=MW2014 />排行榜上每位人士的資產淨值是根據他們的資產與債務來做估計，並以[[美元|美元]]表示。皇族及獨裁者等財富來自於他們的身分地位者將不包含在此排行榜中。<ref name=AL2014/>此排行榜僅登錄實質申報之財產，若其財富來源不明者將不被採計。<ref name="Why Isn’t on ‘Forbes’ List">{{cite web|url=http://www.newsweek.com/why-putin-isnt-forbes-billionaires-list-310818|title=Why Putin Isn’t on 'Forbes' Billionaires List|publisher=[[福布斯|Forbes]]|accessdate=2018-06-14|archive-date=2017-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020091119/http://www.newsweek.com/why-putin-isnt-forbes-billionaires-list-310818|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2022年共有2,668位人士上榜。總體而言，2022年富豪資產淨值總額達12.7兆美元。截至2022年，[[微软|微软]]創辦人[[比尔·盖茨|比尔·盖茨]]在過去過去28年間共上榜22次，而[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]創辦人[[杰弗里·贝索斯|杰弗里·贝索斯]]則四次登上榜首，成為首位千億富豪<ref name="Forbes-2017">{{cite news |url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/money/savingandinvesting/forbes-2017-billionaires-list-meet-the-richest-people-on-the-planet/ar-BByqKfX |title=Forbes 2017 billionaires list: Meet the richest people on the planet |last=Kroll |first=Luisa |work=Forbes |access-date=2017-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321160341/http://www.msn.com/en-us/money/savingandinvesting/forbes-2017-billionaires-list-meet-the-richest-people-on-the-planet/ar-BByqKfX |archive-date=2017-03-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，直至2022年被[[埃隆·马斯克|埃隆·马斯克]]超越。<ref name="FOB22" />

根據[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]報導，500位最富有人士在2017年的資產增長總計達1兆美元。<ref name="BN-20171227">{{cite news |last1=Metcalf |first1=Tom |last2=Witzig |first2=Jack |title=World's Wealthiest Became $1 Trillion Richer in 2017 |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-12-27/world-s-wealthiest-gain-1-trillion-in-17-on-market-exuberance |date=2017-12-27 |work=[[彭博新聞社|Bloomberg News]] |accessdate=2017-12-27 |archive-date=2017-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227073415/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-12-27/world-s-wealthiest-gain-1-trillion-in-17-on-market-exuberance |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="WP-20171227">{{cite news |last=Erickson |first=Amanda |title=The world’s 500 wealthiest people got $1 trillion richer in 2017 |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/12/27/the-worlds-500-wealthiest-people-got-1-trillion-richer-in-2017/ |date=2017-12-27 |work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |accessdate=2017-12-27 |archive-date=2017-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227222508/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/worldviews/wp/2017/12/27/the-worlds-500-wealthiest-people-got-1-trillion-richer-in-2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據[[樂施會|樂施會]]在2017年的一份報告指出，前8位富豪所持有的資產總額已超越全球一半最窮人口的財富。<ref name="OXF-20170116">{{cite news |last=Ratcliff |first=Anna |title=Just 8 men own same wealth as half the world |url=https://www.oxfam.org/en/pressroom/pressreleases/2017-01-16/just-8-men-own-same-wealth-half-world |date=2017-01-16 |work=[[樂施會|Oxfam]] |accessdate=2017-01-16 |archive-date=2017-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116191825/https://www.oxfam.org/en/pressroom/pressreleases/2017-01-16/just-8-men-own-same-wealth-half-world |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20170116">{{cite news |last=Mullany |first=Gerry |title=World’s 8 Richest Have as Much Wealth as Bottom Half of Global Population |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/16/world/eight-richest-wealth-oxfam.html |date=2017-01-16 |work=[[纽约时报|New York Times]] |accessdate=2017-01-16 |