== 統計數據 ==

[[網際網路泡沫|網際網路泡沫]]為一些富豪製造了高額{{le|紙面財富|paper wealth}}。然而，一旦網際網路泡沫消退，這些人士的財富將不復存在。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.economist.com/node/654053|title=A survey of the new rich: The new wealth of nations|work=[[The_Economist|The Economist]]|date=2001-06-14|accessdate=2015-04-02|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226011652/http://www.economist.com/node/654053|dead-url=no}}</ref>富豪的財富又受到[[2008年世界金融危機|2008年世界金融危機]]的影響。2009年是在五年內的首年，全球的富豪數量出現淨虧損。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.economist.com/node/13356686|title=A special report on the rich: Easier for a camel|work=[[The_Economist|The Economist]]|date=2009-04-04|accessdate=2015-04-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110112194744/http://www.economist.com/node/13356686|archivedate=2011-01-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>[[金融市場|金融市場]]的強勁表現與全球經濟復甦已經抹滅了[[金融資產|金融資產]]損失。大多數富有人士的財富在過去幾年內逐漸高漲。<ref name="Global Wealth Report">{{cite web|url=http://www.dasinvestment.com/fileadmin/images/pictures/0907/BCG_2011_0106_Global_Wealth_Report_client_version_May2011.pdf|title=Global Wealth Report 2011|work=[[The_Boston_Consulting_Group|The Boston Consulting Group]]|date=2011-05-31|format=PDF|accessdate=2015-04-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923212754/http://www.dasinvestment.com/fileadmin/images/pictures/0907/BCG_2011_0106_Global_Wealth_Report_client_version_May2011.pdf|archivedate=2015-09-23}}</ref><ref name="World Wealth Report">{{cite web|url=http://www.ml.com/media/114235.pdf|title=World Wealth Report 2011|work=[[Capgemini|Capgemini]] and [[Merrill_Lynch|Merrill Lynch]]|date=2011-06-22|format=PDF|accessdate=2015-04-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103030847/http://ml.com/media/114235.pdf|archivedate=2011-11-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

